open powershell

npm install -g @forge/cli
npm config get prefix -- to get current path

forge login - official acc

forge create 
? Select a context: Confluence
? Select a category: Custom UI
? Select a template: confluence-global-settings

Inside forge :

For the first time
cd static/hello-world
npm install
npm run build
cd ../..
forge deploy
forge install 

Afterwards
cd static/hello-world
npm run build
cd ../..
forge deploy
forge install --upgrade
